### API v1 - Events Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000

### 1. Get All Events
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Create New Event (Admin)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tech Conference 2024",
  "description": "Annual technology conference",
  "event_date": "2024-12-15T10:00:00",
  "total_tickets": 500,
  "max_tickets_per_user": 5
}

### 3. Get Events with Filters
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events?status=upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
